Text: Fw would like to get in touch Original Message From To Sent Monday January AM Subject would like to get in touch This is an automated message from smithcom Do not press reply Someone saw your name on smithcom and wanted to get in touch For your privacy your email is no longer published on the site Heres the info the person supplied Name Tom Pflug Email address There is no one in the smithcom database with this email address If you want to get in touch with this person you should email himher If you dont you can discard this email and do nothing else We at smithcom cannot take responsibility if this person is not who they say they are or for any consequences arising from communicating with this person Thanks for being a part of smithcom Our network is stronger because of you

Fw Welcome to HAZLEWOODS DODGE Original Message From B To Sent Monday January PM Subject Welcome to HAZLEWOODS DODGE Hellomy name is Brenda LockwoodInternet Sales Manager at Hazlewoods Dodge I have received a request that you are looking for a Ram pickup and I would be happy to help you go forward with your new vehicle purchase There are incentives available on the vehicle that you are interested inThey are as follows rebate or special rates of by or months I can be reached at x or via email at Please reply to this email and let me know what you would like to do Sincerely Brenda Lockwood Do You Yahoo Send FREE video emails in Yahoo Mail videomail

Enron Kids Update Cc This afternoon Wednesday we delivered all gift bags to Gordon Elementary for their student Holiday Party on With your help we raised over that we used to sponsor of those children Due to recent company events the Enron Kids Committee had a very difficult time getting sponsors for all the kids but no one was left out We used our remaining charity fund to make sure EVERY child received their gift Though we reduced the sponsor amount by eliminating the shoes and jacket from the gift bags we had enough money left over to purchase gift certificates for shoes for the kids from a national chain store Though a lot of program sponsors were without jobs this holiday season we only had to buy gifts for kids of the total at the last minute this was significantly less than what I had dreaded it might be Thank you for all your help and support Houston children have a better holiday because of you Best Wishes to You All Kevin Hyatt CoChairman Enron Kids Committee

Fw Community Services Association Original Message From WALDEN ON LAKE HOUSTON To Sent Thursday February AM Subject Community Services Association Dear j Kevin Open Directors Position Click Here to retrieve If you cannot click on the link then go to getoffergetoffercfmidemail You received this email from WALDEN ON LAKE HOUSTON because you provided the club with your email address If you do not wish to receive future emails please click here and you will be removed from our database This is a post only mailing Please do not reply to this message

Fw Ford Truck Enthusiasts Original Message From To Sent Tuesday August AM Subject Ford Truck Enthusiasts Thank you for registering to use our forum Following is your login information Your username is TxHusker Your password is bb Please goto cgibindcforumdcboardcgi and select login icon to login Then to change your password click on Settings Icon NOTICE By default your user profile is viewable by other logged in users Additionally other logged in users may email you via your postings If you want to change either of these settings login into the boards and then click the Settings icon to change your user settings Thank you Ken Payne Webmaster Ford Truck Enthusiasts
